{"tid":1588167,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"砂糖倒油缸是毒招  大家千祈唔好咁做呀","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:52:28.000Z","uid":266879,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa69869cec48f0e33078d42a9446e19c7ef12bca","tid":1588167,"uid":266879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPhQQWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPhQQWW.png&h=dea1fa80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】香港汽車工業學會會長李耀培指出，不法分子把砂糖倒進偈油缸以污染小巴引擎，其破壞性比倒入其他物料更嚴重，因砂糖不但堵塞引擎油管，遇熱更會熔化為焦糖，黏附在機件上阻礙運轉，令小巴引擎「死火」，要清洗亦極為困難。他懷疑是熟悉汽車運作者想出此「毒計」損毁小巴。<br />\n堵油管難清理 料要入廠「大修」<br />\n<br />\n遭殃的3輛車包括石油氣及柴油小巴，雖然兩者所用燃料不同，但同樣需要用偈油冷卻及潤滑機件。若偈油混入砂糖，固體砂糖首先會如沙石般堵塞油管，隨着引擎開始運轉，砂糖會受熱融化成糖漿及焦糖，黏附在理應沒有空隙的機件上，磨損零件，同時令引擎過熱，在短時間內「死火」。<br />\n<br />\n李耀培補充，雖然砂糖不會釀成爆炸等危險，惟一旦融化並黏上機件，幾乎無法清除，恐要把受污染零件全數更換，行內稱「大修」，費用高昂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://larid.hk/view5/21234/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flarid.hk%2Fview5%2F21234%2F&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly%2FZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=2e3b1a33\" target=\"_blank\">http://larid.hk/view5/21234/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4058ddbaf7746016b1323d134802e2cd10458701","tid":1588167,"uid":58088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cae98614f3e09aacaa95438da2ee4ca4a9330c","tid":1588167,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"咪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警車咪好危險"},{"pid":"8019a7c2519de767463cb1f11c66cb39e7457501","tid":1588167,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":